<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,151,686]" pageId="5" pageNumber="391">
Female genitalia: Oviscape black (
<quantity box="[620,720,152,176]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.9" pageId="5" pageNumber="391" unit="mm" value="1.9">1.9 mm</quantity>
); eversible membrane (
<quantity box="[1006,1103,152,176]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.7" pageId="5" pageNumber="391" unit="mm" value="1.7">1.7 mm</quantity>
) with spicules of eversible membrane having single pointed projection, aculeus (
<quantity box="[751,839,188,212]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.4" pageId="5" pageNumber="391" unit="mm" value="1.4">1.4 mm</quantity>
) with apex forked and four pairs of preapical setae.
</paragraph>
